# Hackathon Rules

- All code must be new (written after April 24, 2026)
- Working demo required (2-4 min video)
- Max 3 sponsor prize applications
- Public GitHub repo with README
- Document AI tool usage (which files/features were AI-assisted)
- Commit early and often — judges check git history

# Judging Criteria (All Sponsors)
- Does it work?
- Real utility over novelty
- Depth of sponsor integration
- Code quality and documentation
- Clear demo video

# Sponsor Targets
1. Gensyn (AXL) — P2P agent communication
2. KeeperHub — on-chain execution layer
3. x402 — HTTP 402 micropayments
4. 0G — decentralized storage and compute
5. Uniswap v4 — custom swap hooks
